dc_title_s: Land Use St. Croix County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data layer represents land use for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NSt_Croix_LandUse_2018.gdbN. [The proposed land use classification identified during community planning activities and sometimes defined at the parcel level, but typically proposed land use units are larger than the parcel.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: St. Croix County Land Use, Planning and Development
